{"url": "https://book.douban.com/subject/1000153/", "id": "1000153", "title": "印象主义创始者:马奈", "cover": "https://img3.doubanio.com/view/subject/l/public/s1000102.jpg", "base": "作者: 何政广出版社:河北教育出版社出版年:2000-12页数:183定价:78.00装帧:平装丛书: 世界名画家全集ISBN:9787543439337", "intro": "19世纪印象派的产生是西洋美术发展史上极为重要的一个转折点，而此流派的奠基人，即是主张“为艺术而艺术”的法国绘画大师——马奈。虽然他从未真正参加印象派的展览，但他深具革新精神的艺术创作态度，却深深影响了莫奈，塞尚、凡·高等新兴画家，进而将绘画带入现代主义的道路上。受到日本浮世绘及西班牙画风的影响，马奈大胆采用鲜明色彩，舍弃传统绘画的中间色彩，将绘画从追求三元次立体空间的传统束缚中解放出来，朝二元次的平面创作迈出革命性的一大步。此外，马奈亦以自然主义式的想像来处理创作的题材与构图，并未刻意美化，取而代之的是清晰、冷静、光线均匀分布的景致，表现出和谐、清楚而简约的风格。马奈在绘画生涯的大胆创新，影响深远，在美术史上可谓占有举足轻重的地位。本书为2001年5月第2次印刷。", "tags": ["艺术", "画册", "马奈", "美术", "印象派", "法国", "艺术/建筑", "艺术设计"], "score": {"avg": " 7.8 ", "scroe_num": "92", "rating": ["23.9%", "46.7%", "28.3%", "1.1%", "0.0%"]}, "comments": [{"comment_id": "40514066", "nick_name": "何倩彤", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/tenkappa/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1003853-196.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">still my favourite</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "79257715", "nick_name": "孬爷爷", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/post-rocker/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1203352-499.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">套装</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "55794179", "nick_name": "KAKHABERVNA", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2143112/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u2143112-48.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2008-08-23", "content": "<span class=\"short\">以前我一直误解马奈</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "10029843", "nick_name": "还有什么更好的", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/1201841/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1201841-3.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2007-02-02", "content": "<span class=\"short\">开始慢慢往外走了</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "180514363", "nick_name": "HUAIHAI", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/HUAIHAI/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2422845-272.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2009-12-12", "content": "<span class=\"short\">马奈其实蛮古典的。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "722651109", "nick_name": "崔", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/cui_ning/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34864208-10.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">贝尔特·莫里索很漂亮</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "68983118", "nick_name": "罗伯特小姐", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/missrobert/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1657082-5.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2008-10-29", "content": "<span class=\"short\">双重人格的天真现实主义者\r\n\r\n</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "52982036", "nick_name": "锦~鲤", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/mivo/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2050144-122.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2008-08-05", "content": "<span class=\"short\">也是站着看完的\r\n</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "333381443", "nick_name": "莱斯基", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/Laisky/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u3068199-19.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2010-12-30", "content": "<span class=\"short\">介绍和图有些搭不上，语言有一些逻辑错误，然后有些图的原图和局部图出处不同，不太了解是怎么回事，从画面上明显能看出细节不一致，但是没有相关介绍…</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "681008979", "nick_name": "萨宾娜的圆礼帽", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/bmg12345/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u56768502-6.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2013-05-16", "content": "<span class=\"short\">我能说马奈的构图有点散乱么</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "417700153", "nick_name": "April", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/damndreamer/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2786635-54.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "", "comment_time": "", "content": "<span class=\"short\">对马奈而言接受印象派始祖和死不承认这一头衔分别意味着什么阿?</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1290554313", "nick_name": "林逸凡", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/oyster_world/", "head_image": "https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u71930749-7.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2017-12-22", "content": "<span class=\"short\">印象派创始人，但始终不认为属于印象派。早期画风比较自然写实，后来开始在日本画中学会平抹技法，在画法上开始用色块堆积或涂抹。马奈的画很少被沙龙展认可，在自我跟别人看法中矛盾。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1366408531", "nick_name": "林鸫", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/123965345/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u123965345-5.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2018-04-30", "content": "<span class=\"short\">构图不行\n</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1625241717", "nick_name": "牧城", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/thisisgap/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u66635617-3.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2019-01-13", "content": "<span class=\"short\">这文字的排版把装帧全毁了</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "549341351", "nick_name": "fish·li", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/26399682/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u26399682-10.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar30 rating", "comment_time": "2012-06-27", "content": "<span class=\"short\">说句实话，不怎么样，讲的很浅，画的颜色也不正，随便看看即可</span>\n            "}], "reviews": [{"review_id": "5518587", "review_title": "“分裂”的马奈", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u31678134-3.jpg", "nick_name": "King", "review_score": "allstar50 main-title-rating", "review_time": "2012-07-24 10:04:57", "review_content": "<div class=\"main-bd\">\n\n\n    \n  \n    \n\n    <div id=\"link-report\">\n      <div class=\"review-content clearfix\" data-author=\"King\" data-url=\"https://book.douban.com/review/5518587/\" data-original=\"1\">\n        <p>　　１８６３年，当《草地上的晚餐》出现在公众眼前时，一个新时代诞生了，虽然近代绘画的源泉非常的久远，但严格意义上的出现便是这幅画，而马奈也就成为印象主义乃至近现代绘画的直接创始者。\n　　其实这对马奈来说是一个讽刺，可以这样说，马奈在这方面算得上精神分裂了。马奈出身和思想都是保守的。一辈子想得到中产阶级的承认，所以从不参加印象派画展，也不承认自己是印象派（其实印象派也不承认他，只是推崇他的创新），这点与福楼拜（写《包法利夫人》后）相同。但显然他的心与手和他的思想是分裂的，当《奥林匹亚》出现在公众面前时，整个中产阶级都愤怒了。可是伟大本来就是如此，庸人永远是被引导的。只是马奈没有完全忽视公众。使得后期的作品颇受影响。真是可惜了。不管怎么说，马奈是个划时代的人物。</p><p></p>\n      </div>\n\n      \n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n        <div class=\"copyright\">\n          © 本文版权归作者           <a href=\"https://www.douban.com/people/31678134/\">King</a>           所有，任何形式转载请联系作者。\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"main-author\">\n      \n  \n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n      \n  ", "use_num": "\n      有用 1\n  ", "nouse_num": "\n      没用 0\n  ", "review_share": "", "review_reward": "0", "review_comments": []}]}